 The hologram looked at the scorpion. His eyes blinked. Itwas alright now. 
"You may search whatever you wish from my computers. Bue please I wish that 
you would press the butto my base is very vulnerable and i wish it not so 
longer then needed.

 AS they spoke a small pod had teatached from the side of the ship. It 
burrowed into the ground and heaed towards the location of drillbit sending a 
message to him every 30 seconds. "Old friend I am alive I need your help." 
The protoform in the pod wouldnt last long away from the ship unless a beast 
mode was made soon. Unfortunatly the mekanizim that controls it had broken 
and need to be done manualy by the outside. The pod made its way towards 
drill bits location.

--part1_a5.106679bc.2799fceb_boundary
